            <header class="page-header">
                <h1>About Gereja Katolik Damai Kristus – Paroki Kampung Duri</h1>
                <p>A welcoming Catholic community serving with faith and love since 1987.</p>
            </header>

            <section class="about-section">
                <div class="content-box">
                    <h3><i class="fas fa-bullseye"></i> Our Mission</h3>
                    <p>
                        The Catholic Church of Christ the Peace – Kampung Duri is a faith-filled community centered on Christ, united in love and service. We are committed to growing in faith, deepening our spiritual life, and sharing the peace of Christ with everyone. We invite all to join us in prayer, ministry, and fellowship, that together we may become living witnesses of Christ’s love and joy in the world.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="about-section">
                <div class="content-box">
                    <h3><i class="fas fa-heart"></i> Our Values</h3>
                    <ul class="values-list">
                        <li><strong>Faith:</strong> Deepening our relationship with God through prayer, worship, and the sacraments</li>
                        <li><strong>Community:</strong> Building lasting relationships and supporting one another</li>
                        <li><strong>Service:</strong> Reaching out to those in need with compassion and love</li>
                        <li><strong>Growth:</strong> Continuous learning and spiritual development for all ages</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="about-section-grid">
                <div class="content-box">
                    <h3><i class="fas fa-users"></i> Our Community</h3>
                    <p>
                        We are a diverse community of over 1,200 families from various backgrounds, united in faith and committed to serving God and one another.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="content-box">
                    <h3><i class="fas fa-book-open"></i> Faith Formation</h3>
                    <p>
                        We offer comprehensive religious education programs for children, youth, and adults, including sacramental preparation and Bible study groups.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="about-section">
                <div class="content-box pastor-box">
                    <h3><i class="fas fa-user-tie"></i> Our Pastor</h3>
                    <div class="pastor-info">
                        <div class="pastor-avatar">
                            <span>MW</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="pastor-details">
                            <h4>Fr. Matheus Widyolestari</h4>
                            <span>Pastor</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <p class="pastor-bio">
                        Father Matheus Widyolestari, MSC has been serving the parish of Gereja Damai Kristus – Kampung Duri since 2018. With a deep passion for evangelization and compassionate pastoral care, he is dedicated to nurturing the faith and unity of the parish community, guiding families in their spiritual journey, and extending Christ’s love to all who seek hope and belonging.
                    </p>
                </div>
